[B]Default keys: (for version 1.0 and up [U]only![/U])[/B]

Bar 4:
1 - Devouring Plague/Desperate Prayer
2 - Psychic Scream
3 - Touch of Weakness/Shadowmeld/Shadowguard/Fear Ward
4 - Vampiric Embrace
5 - Vampiric Touch
6 - Fade
7 - Bandage
8 - Shadow Fiend
9 - SW: Death
0 - Will of the Forsaken (UD Only)

Bar 5:
1 - Mind Blast
2 - Mind Flay (CooldownProbe[Spell here must NOT have a cooldown, but gcd must apply])
3 - SW: Pain
4 - PW: Shield
5 - Renew
6 - Flash Heal
7 - Wand
8 - Inner Focus
9 - Shadow Form
0 - Silence
- - Potion
= - Mana Burn

Bar 6:
1 - PW: Fortitude
2 - Inner Fire
3 - Dispel Magic
4 - Greater Heal
5 - Cure Disease
6 - Item 1
7 - Item 2
8 - Bandage
9 - Eat
0 - Drink
- - Mount
= - HS


